ðŸŸ¦ Tier 2 â€“ Short-term Staking (1â€“2 months)

Benefits:

- Earn the standard APY (e.g., 90%).

- Join the pre-sale after the long-term staking round.

- Receive 2% fee rewards from tokens paired with $ZC during pre-sales.

- Restake immediately after maturity to gain a +5% APY bonus for the next cycle.


4. Lock & Buyback Mechanism

- After each pre-sale, tokens are locked for only 1 week.

- 50% of post-listing sell fees are used to buy back to support price stability.

- Buybacks are triggered only when token < SMA7 (7-day average price) for cost efficiency.

- During the first week post-listing (Guardian Week):

  + Trading fees (buy/sell) are doubled to discourage snipers & jeeters.

  + After 7 days, all fees automatically revert to normal.


